| | ... | Set Acl List For Interface | ${dut} | ${dut_if2} | input | ${acl_list}
| | Run Keyword If | 'output' in $acl_apply_type and $dut_if1 is not None
| | ... | Set Acl List For Interface | ${dut} | ${dut_if1} | output
| | ... | ${acl_list}
